reviews.title: Ads aren\'t free...
reviews.comment: I understand the ads on a free app, but my baby signed me up for a $10 subscription app. I also understand that I need to monitor her while she\'s using it, but part of the point of this app is to keep her occupied for a minute while I\'m trying to do something else. I\'ve now learned how to put a pin on purchases so it doesn\'t happen again.
